{"word":"εἰσμαίομαι","slug":"εἰσμαίομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n31431\" key=\"ei)smai/omai\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">εἰσμαίομαι</orth>, used by <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author> </bibl> only in <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ep.\">Ep.</a></gram> </gramGrp> <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ aor.\">aor.</a></tns> I, <sense id=\"n31431.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">touch to the quick, affect greatly,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">μάλα γάρ με θανὼν ἐσεμάσσατο θυμόν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:17:564\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">17.564</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὃς ἐμόν γε μάλιστ᾽ ἐσεμάσσατο θυμόν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:20:425\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">20.425</biblScope></bibl></cit>.—The <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ pres.\">pres.</a></tns> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">εἰσμαίομαι</foreign> is not found, cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐπιμαίομαι, εἰσματέομαι.</foreign> </sense> </entryFree>"}]}